TY  - JOUR
T1  - A Note on Asset Proportions, Stochastic Dominance, and the 50% Rule
AU  - Clark, Ephraim
AU  - Jokung, Octave
Y1  - 1999/12/01
PY  - 1999
DA  - 1999/12/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.45.12.1724
